											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Karlach (as a mind flayer) wraps their tentacles around Orpheus' face and brings their mouth over Orpheus' head. &#xD;&#xA;Karlach feeds CLUMSILY. Suckling noises.&#xD;&#xA;Orpheus' eyes dart around in pain as his brain is consumed.&#xD;&#xA;Once it's done, Orpheus' head flops to the side, his head empty. " />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
