											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Karlach does a mindmeld effect and telepathically absorbs the tadpole. As they do so, the tadpole turns to particles that move towards their head, leaving nothing behind. Once the tadpole is absorbed, Karlach turns into mind flayer. Reference gameplay animation that exists, but more elaborate and cinematic. " />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
