											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The Emperor produces the |supreme tadpole|, psionically levitates it in his hand. &#xD;&#xA;With a gesture of his hand, mind flayer psionically moves Karlach's hand up, palm out, ready to receive.&#xD;&#xA;Mind flayer hand drops tadpole in Karlach's palm.&#xD;&#xA;Shot of supreme tadpole squirming in Karlach's palm. &#xD;&#xA;Shot o Karlach's expression reacting to it. " />
